  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat. ",
    "Season the chicken breasts with salt, black pepper, and lime zest. ",
    "Grill the chicken for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through. ",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together basil leaves, cilantro, lime juice, avocado oil, garlic, salt, and black pepper. ",
    "Add the grilled chicken to the bowl and toss with the herb mixture. ",
    "Garnish with fresh mint leaves and serve with lime wedges. ",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with fresh herbs. ",
    "Garnish with additional basil leaves and serve with lime wedges. ",
    "Garnish with additional mint leaves. "
